high_descs: Look down, turn right and walk straight to the desk and look down again.
Pick up the pen on the desk.
Look up, turn around and walk to the other side of the desk to your right where the mug is placed.
Place the pen inside the mug.
Pick up the mug with the pen inside.
Turn around, and walk to the clothing cabinet to the far left next to the bed.
Place the mug next to the phone on top of the clothing cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pen inside on top of the clothing cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the desk.
Pick up the pen on the desk.
Bring the pen to the mug on the right side of the desk.
Put the pen in the mug on the desk.
Pick up the mug with pencil on the desk.
Bring the mug with pencil right to the tall dresser next to the bed.
Put the mug with pencil on the top of the dresser, left of the phone.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with pencil on the dresser, left of the phone.

high_descs: Turn to your right and approach the black chair.
Pick up the pen from the desk.
Turn around to look at the door then turn right and walk to the wall, then back to the desk.
Put the pen into the cup.
Pick up the pen with the pen in it.
Turn around then walk to the left to the chest of drawers.
Place the cup on the chest of drawers to the left of the phone.
anns.task_desc: Move a pen and cup from the desk to the chest of drawers.
